flowchart TD
    A[Applicant opens apply.php] --> B{Logged in + applicant role?}
    B -->|No| C[Redirect login/index]
    B -->|Yes| D{Open application period exists?}
    D -->|No| E[Show application closed]
    D -->|Yes| F{Already applied this period?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Block duplicate application]
    F -->|No| H[Load wizard state from session + persistent draft]

    H --> I[Step 1: Applicant and school info]
    I --> J[save_step1 + autosave]
    J --> K[Step 2: Personal and family info]
    K --> L[save_step2 + autosave]
    L --> M[Step 3: Siblings, education, grants]
    M --> N[save_step3 + autosave]
    N --> O[Step 4: Upload requirement documents]
    O --> P{Required docs present?}
    P -->|No| O
    P -->|Yes| Q[save_step4 + autosave]
    Q --> R[Step 5/Photo page apply-photo.php]
    R --> S{2x2 photo captured/uploaded?}
    S -->|No| R
    S -->|Yes| T[Save cropped photo path]
    T --> U[Step 6: Review and final submit]
    U --> V{Recheck period + duplicate + required fields/docs/photo}
    V -->|Fail| U
    V -->|Pass| W[Insert applications row status=under_review]
    W --> X[Move temp photo/docs to final uploads folders]
    X --> Y[Insert application_documents rows]
    Y --> Z[Create notification + send submission SMS]
    Z --> AA[Clear wizard session + persistent draft]
    AA --> AB[Redirect my-application.php]
